Ext.data.JsonP['Installing_a_Plugin']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Installing a Plugin</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083269\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Installing a Plugin</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083269_InstallingaPlugin-Contents\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Contents</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Installing_a_Plugin-section-src-30083269_InstallingaPlugin-Overview\">Overview</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Installing_a_Plugin-section-src-30083269_InstallingaPlugin-Installing3rdPartyPluginsintoStudio\">Installing 3rd Party Plugins into Studio</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083269_InstallingaPlugin-Overview\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Overview</span></h2>\n    <p>You can add more functionality to Studio by installing one of the many compatible plugins--Studio itself is available as both a standalone application and an Eclipse plugin.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083269_InstallingaPlugin-Installing3rdPartyPluginsintoStudio\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Installing 3rd Party Plugins into Studio</span></h2>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Go to <strong class=\" \">Help</strong> -&gt; <strong class=\" \">Install New Software...</strong>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>In the &quot;Work with:&quot; text box, specify the desired update site for the 3rd party plugin.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">Add...</strong>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Specify the Name of the Update site (i.e. New Software Plugin).    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">OK</strong>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select the top level checkbox in the table below.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">Next</strong> Button.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Confirm the items you are installing.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">Next</strong> Button once more.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Accept the terms and conditions.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">Finish</strong> Button.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083269\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Installing a Plugin"});